OL,3,CFamily of aid worker killed in Gaza
OL,4,Ccall for independent inquiry
OL,6,FThe family of a Bristol aid worker
OL,7,Fkilled by an Israeli drone strike in
OL,8,FGaza have urged the Government to hold
OL,9,Fan independent inquiry into his death.
OL,11,FJames Kirby, 47, was one of seven
OL,12,FWorld Central Kitchen workers fatally
OL,13,Finjured in the attack, including two
OL,14,Fother Britons - John Chapman, from
OL,15,FDorset, and James "Jim" Henderson from
OL,16,FCornwall.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/9
