OL,3,CFamily of aid worker killed in Gaza
OL,4,Ccall for independent inquiry
OL,6,FThe group was travelling in a World
OL,7,FCentral Kitchen convoy leaving one of
OL,8,Fits warehouses when Israeli armed
OL,9,Fdrones fired munitions at their marked
OL,10,Fvehicles on 1 April this year.
OL,12,FA memorial service for Mr Kirby, who
OL,13,Fpreviously served with the Rifles,
OL,14,Fwill take place at Bristol Cathedral
OL,15,Fon Wednesday 4 September.
