OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F431A1725443743
OL,3,CFamily of aid worker killed in Gaza
OL,4,Ccall for independent inquiry
OL,6,F"The state of Israel says the murder
OL,7,Fwas an accident. So we were surprised
OL,8,Fnot to have had any contact or
OL,9,Fcondolence from Israel's ambassador to
OL,10,Fthe UK in London, nor from any Israeli
OL,11,Fofficial.
OL,13,F"Any family of a loved one who has
OL,14,Fbeen killed needs closure. We need to
OL,15,Funderstand how this disaster could
OL,16,Fhave happened.
OL,18,F"But this is not just about us.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUzD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/9
