OL,3,CFamily of aid worker killed in Gaza
OL,4,Ccall for independent inquiry
OL,6,F"This is about how Britain looks after
OL,7,Fits own citizens and their families,
OL,8,Fwhen a British citizen has been
OL,9,Funlawfully killed by another state.
OL,11,F"There must be a proper, independent
OL,12,Finquiry into this attack on innocent
OL,13,Faid workers, and for the evidence to
OL,14,Fbe assessed, if appropriate, in a
OL,15,Frelevant court of law."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUwD@WO]
