OL,3,CFamily of aid worker killed in Gaza
OL,4,Ccall for independent inquiry
OL,6,FThe relief team's leader, Australian
OL,7,Fnational Lalzawmi "Zomi" Frankcom, 43,
OL,8,Falso died, with dual American-Canadian
OL,9,Fcitizen Jacob Flickinger, 33; Polish
OL,10,Fnational Damian Sobol, 35; and their
OL,11,Fdriver, Palestinian Saifeddin Issam
OL,12,FAyad Abutaha, 25.
OL,14,FThe Israel Defence Forces dismissed
OL,15,Ftwo officers and reprimanded three
OL,16,Fothers, calling the deadly attack a
OL,17,F"serious mistake".
OL,19,FMs Kirby said the families of those
OL,20,Fwho died had not received contact from
OL,21,Fthe UK Government since the deaths.
OL,26,@oD@SOUoD@XO]yD@AOUyD@QO]
