OL,3,CFamily of aid worker killed in Gaza
OL,4,Ccall for independent inquiry
OL,6,FThey also have not had any information
OL,7,Fon whether a "credible, independent
OL,8,Finvestigation is taking place", or the
OL,9,Fresults of any investigation if it has
OL,10,Falready taken place, she added.
OL,12,FShe said: "We appreciate the
OL,13,Fcompassion and respect we have been
OL,14,Fshown, but we must also have
OL,15,Ftransparency and accountability. How
OL,16,Fdid this happen? Who is responsible?
OL,17,FWhat accountability did they face?
OL,26,@oD@NOUpD@^O]tD@KOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/9
