OL,6,FMs Kirby added: "I very much hope the
OL,7,FPrime Minister will take our concerns
OL,8,Fseriously and instigate an
OL,9,Fappropriate, independent or legal
OL,10,Finquiry, not only so we can have
OL,11,Ftransparency and accountability, but
OL,12,Fso that other British citizens and
OL,13,Ftheir families know that their
OL,14,Fgovernment will act for them, if a
OL,15,Fforeign state unlawfully kills their
OL,16,Floved ones."
OL,26,@nD@QOUxD@LO]
